message.body: I guess I can do lunch and dinner walk on Sunday. I think Michelle can do Saturday but check with her.
It's Sat & Sun lunch walks and Sat dinner walk/feeding. I can do Sun night.
Ok I'll do lunch and dinner on Saturday 14th
Ok, great. Michelle should be able to do Sunday lunch.
Oh, that's good. Maybe when you're up to it, we can hang again. Didn't really get to catch up much the other night.
Yeah, I'm sorry about that. We will have to do it again when I'm feeling myself. Hope u r hanging in there too
Nothing to be sorry about. It's always nice being with you. I'm feeling pretty good. It's been a quiet few days which is nice.
